0:10:43.352,000 --> 0:10:44,000
that's committed to work through partners

271
0:10:45.247,000 --> 0:10:47,000
and help improve the lives and protect the rights

272
0:10:47.87,000 --> 0:10:49,000
of 100 million children by 2015.

273
0:10:50.737,000 --> 0:10:51,000
You know the phrase,

274
0:10:52.413,000 --> 0:10:55,000
you can manage what you measure?

