0:12:04.357,000 --> 0:12:05,000
Vote with your wallets.

300
0:12:06.055,000 --> 0:12:08,000
Search out the companies

301
0:12:08.235,000 --> 0:12:1,000
that are acting on this.

302
0:12:10.93,000 --> 0:12:13,000
